{"title":"从世纪的边缘地带走来","authors":["常敬竹"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":9,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"从世纪的边缘地带走来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常敬竹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着世纪的边缘地带"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们走进１９８９"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的渴望与想象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在挥手之间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推开一方蔚蓝的天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"致意这片神奇的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和土地上泥土般淳朴的民意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清新的风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹过肃穆的红墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悠扬的晨钟一阵阵激越生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾经驰骋疆场的老兵们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把枪和军号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"递给你们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座座里程碑站在路边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默默地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送你们启程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论走出多远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走到哪里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们也不会忘记身后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火一样燃烧的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灿烂的阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温柔地抚摸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芳菲的大草原和白桦林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抚摸你们宽阔的前额"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时你们以普通人的步履"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在美丽的家园里行走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们以亲子的身份"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在老区戴起乡亲的斗笠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在上海狭窄的里弄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叩响寻常百姓的门扉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在八十高龄的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次次拜访邻居"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记忆穿越森林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在真实的阳光和空气里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻颤栗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们以睿智的思辨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"营造着东方与西方的连线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"探究言辞以外的含义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对于未来世纪的曙光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们正一丝一缕地把握"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界因你们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而回复"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对一种肤色的健康认识"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的土地上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生长着坚韧的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十一亿胸腔的心声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"澎湃如黄河长江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有民众以同一种心情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"期待史诗和天使的火炬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"期待太阳船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牵引今天的视线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和明天的记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为少女肩头的白鸽子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚守一片净土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"期待是一副沉重的担子呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让你们血性的肩头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担着人生之旅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵然岁月迢遥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天涯路远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们执著的脚步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依旧无悔地实践当初的诺言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们深邃的目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹如坚实的铁路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正驮着一个民族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏歌而去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：中央警卫团）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}